==Gamilaraay==
===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|/ŋaja/}}
===Etymology===
From Proto-Central New South Wales ''*ngaya'', from Proto-Pama-Nyungan ''*ngayu ~ *ngayi ~ *ngaya''.
===Pronoun===
'''ngaya'''

# [[I]] (''first person nominative singular pronoun'')
